        "zh": "1.職業安全衛生法規簡介<br>2.職業災害之雇主責任與勞工權益<br>3.職業安全衛生教育訓練<br>4.勞工健康檢查與管理<br>5.職業災害調查與處理<br>6.機械設備與安全<br>7.噪音危害<br>8.化學性危害<br>9.危害通識<br>10.職業病防治<br>",
        "en": "1.Occupational Safety and Health Act Statute<br>2.Responsibility of Employer &amp; Protection for Workers Incurring Occupational Accidents<br>3.Education &amp; Training for Occupational Safety and Health<br>4.Inspection and Management for Labor Health<br>5.Investigation &amp; Measures for Occupational Accidents<br>6.Equipment Safety<br>7.Noise Hazard<br>8.Chemical Hazard<br>9.Hazard Communication<br>10.Occupational Disease Control<br>"
